{"tid":231392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想捐血咪捐，唔想捐咪唔捐，有乜好嘈？但我唔明關334乜事","createTime":"2017-05-06T04:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T06:38:34.000Z","uid":37300,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0fa60c61c4b76dac445dee620f0764d90b76e92","tid":231392,"uid":37300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:13:45.000Z","msg":"舊制：<br />\n中4中6我當1.5級，中5中7都係1.5級，但中5中7得半年所以1.5/2=0.75級，總共2.25級可以捐血<br />\n<br />\n新制：<br />\n中4中5已經2級，中六0.5級，即係共2.5級<br />\n<br />\n理論上中學可提供血液班級數目比舊制多0.25級，所以理論上同學制無關（學校唔俾佢地入兩次就唔關學制事，係學校問題）<br />\n<br />\n同時紅十字會只係話人數減少，佢地有講香港人口老化，所以需求上升，但人口老化除左長命左，仲講緊出生率下降，即係供應都會跌，佢有冇考慮學童人數減少呢個因素？<br />\n<br />\n如果佢要呢個理由站得住腳，係應該公佈捐血人數佔該年齡層%（甚至年份例如1970-1979，1980-1989，咁樣可以免卻年齡層轉型問題，例如由20-29變左30-39）而唔係就咁講人數？<br />\n<br />\n下圖係捐血人數年齡百分比<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ga5F0T6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fga5F0T6.jpg&h=d953c8ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下圖係2016年人口統計百分比<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/82Ja0t0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F82Ja0t0.jpg&h=a16be3cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e73c0049db0ed1b08c4c87abc44bf6653f3a8088","tid":231392,"uid":37300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:32:04.000Z","msg":"16-20約4.5%人口捐左13.3%<br />\n<br />\n21-30約13%人口捐左27.8%<br />\n<br />\n31-40約15.6%人口捐左24%<br />\n<br />\n41-50約15.5%人口捐20.4%<br />\n<br />\n51-60約17.1%人口捐12.8%<br />\n<br />\n我當51-60歲機能衰退（其實而家醫學昌明，退得幾多），捐得最少%理論上係41-50歲同31-40呢兩類人，即係中年及接近中年，16-20同21-30個數理論上最好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd6ef4e2b0d0421d3d0ba37062a49d09b3d1330","tid":231392,"uid":14131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:35:06.000Z","msg":"巴打你咁認真既<br />\n好簡單，每個年代都係咁嫁啦<br />\n屌完80後屌90後，而家終於開始屌00後<br />\n總之後生就係錯嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bd5ece3a250bce03d6359132546e07ce4077ec","tid":231392,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人口老化呀，越嚟越多既老人係寶，越嚟越稀少既後生係草，遲啲仲有全民保老，你身體每一寸都係為供養老人而生，唔鬧你鬧邊個，鬼叫你遲出世"},{"pid":"2e16073d1b0a91fbcb4900b731ca8167334f1379","tid":231392,"uid":37300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:49:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你咁認真既<br />\n好簡單，每個年代都係咁嫁啦<br />\n屌完80後屌90後，而家終於開始屌00後<br />\n總之後生就係錯嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n30歲或以下人口得17-18%，佔左血副供應量成41%多dd，你話唔夠多人呢個係事實，但明明數據最差唔係呢班人，除非佢認為呢班人最易氹/呃，否則唔應該呢D地方「落廣告」"},{"pid":"e76d1a8f4974181f3a9dd5e2bbeff769852c2598","tid":231392,"uid":37300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225298f99c61d62a52ecbe75a2c4bf447c5021a6","tid":231392,"uid":54371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880073c2916b63164c3c0f1683e1cf47010dd67b","tid":231392,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:05:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你咁認真既<br />\n好簡單，每個年代都係咁嫁啦<br />\n屌完80後屌90後，而家終於開始屌00後<br />\n總之後生就係錯嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nExact7ly，廢中廢老要屌後生去掩飾自己廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fdae47d00e941de66053ae08f73bf85c5ebf3e","tid":231392,"uid":37300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T06:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2388468f6f90a4f1d5ef05682e32791a663b428b","tid":231392,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T06:38:34.000Z","msg":"首先唔多關334事<br />\n第二佢唔好屌自己廢？紅十字會每次嚟，我嗰form每班都有幾個去，搞到最後全form得幾條友捐到，好多去呆坐完就話唔夠時間唔洗捐，怪邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}